Design a premium HSBC-style supplier-side sustainability transition portal called “Supplier Transition Workspace”. This is a dedicated portal for suppliers who have received a sustainability transition notification from a large enterprise client after Scope 3 emissions analysis identified them as high-impact or high-risk contributors.

The portal should feel like: “A guided sustainability transformation workspace powered by HSBC” —not an ESG dashboard.

This is the supplier-facing experience where suppliers:

understand why they were flagged

receive a detailed AI-generated transition roadmap

learn how to reduce emissions

connect with consultants and service providers

discover green technologies

explore certifications

access government subsidies

evaluate HSBC green financing

contact HSBC relationship managers

connect with implementation partners

request quotations from vendors


The experience should feel:

highly supportive

educational

actionable

enterprise-grade

trustworthy

operational

banking-backed

transformation-oriented


